<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 12:25:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>谁是巴基斯坦争取分裂国家的少数民族武装分子？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/who-are-pakistans-ethnic-militants-fighting-secession-2024-08-26/</link><description>官员周一表示，分离主义武装分子在巴基斯坦俾路支省发动了数起协同袭击，造成至少 39 人死亡，这是多年来民族叛乱分子发起的最大规模袭击事件。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 11:21:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/who-are-pakistans-ethnic-militants-fighting-secession-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>印尼与美国举行年度联合军演</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/indonesia-us-hold-annual-joint-military-exercises-2024-08-26/</link><description>印度尼西亚和美国周一开始为期两周的年度军事演习，有超过 4,500 名人员参加，旨在提高作战技能，因为华盛顿寻求在中国争夺影响力的地区加强关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 10:53:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/indonesia-us-hold-annual-joint-military-exercises-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国PDD控股未达季度收入预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/temu-owner-pdd-holdings-misses-quarterly-revenue-estimates-2024-08-26/</link><description>中国拼多多控股周一的季度营收未达到市场预期，原因是消费者支出减少削弱了其国内电子商务平台拼多多的业务，导致该公司股价在盘前交易中下跌 15%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 10:36:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/temu-owner-pdd-holdings-misses-quarterly-revenue-estimates-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：降息希望遭遇中东风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-08-26/</link><description>达拉·拉纳辛格 (Dhara Ranasinghe) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 10:02:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>日本出动战机紧急起飞攻击侵犯领空的中国飞机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/japan-scrambles-jets-against-china-reconnaissance-plane-that-breached-airspace-2024-08-26/</link><description>日本防卫省表示，周一上午，一架中国侦察机短暂侵犯日本领空，日本防卫省已紧急紧急升空。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 09:21:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/japan-scrambles-jets-against-china-reconnaissance-plane-that-breached-airspace-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国滴滴出行正在洽谈向国家支持的四维图新旗下子公司出售智能汽车资产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-didi-talks-sell-smart-auto-assets-state-backed-navinfos-unit-say-sources-2024-08-26/</link><description>三名消息人士称，中国滴滴出行正在就将其智能驾驶和座舱资产出售给国家支持的数字地图公司四维图新旗下子公司进行深入谈判，因为这家网约车公司在经历了严厉的监管打击后专注于其核心业务。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 07:14:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-didi-talks-sell-smart-auto-assets-state-backed-navinfos-unit-say-sources-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>比利时UCB以6.8亿美元出售中国神经病学、过敏业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/belgiums-ucb-sell-china-neurology-allergy-business-680-mln-2024-08-26/</link><description>比利时生物制药公司 UCB 周一表示，将以 6.8 亿美元的价格将其中国神经病学和过敏业务出售给新加坡资产管理集团 CBC 和阿布扎比主权投资者 Mubadala。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 06:17:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/belgiums-ucb-sell-china-neurology-allergy-business-680-mln-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国机器人大会聚焦类人机器人不断变化的面貌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-robots-conference-spotlights-changing-face-humanoids-2024-08-26/</link><description>随着中国寻求在人形机器人开发方面取得领先，其供应链在北京举行的世界机器人大会上展示了更便宜和创新的零部件，但一些高管警告称，该行业尚未提高产品可靠性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 06:09:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-robots-conference-spotlights-changing-face-humanoids-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国工业界寻求缓解拜登-哈里斯对中国关税的大幅上调</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-industry-seeks-easing-steep-biden-harris-china-tariff-hikes-2024-08-26/</link><description>拜登-哈里斯政府预计将于本周宣布对某些中国进口商品大幅提高关税的最终实施计划，如果美国工业如愿，许多计划中的关税将得到软化。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 05:07:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-industry-seeks-easing-steep-biden-harris-china-tariff-hikes-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国在南海的举动具有侵略性且非法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-actions-south-china-sea-patently-illegal-philippine-defence-min-says-2024-08-26/</link><description>过去一周发生一系列空中和海上冲突和事件后，菲律宾政府周一谴责中国在南海“一再采取侵略性、不专业和非法的”行动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 02:20:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-actions-south-china-sea-patently-illegal-philippine-defence-min-says-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国军队将在中缅边境举行武装巡逻和实弹演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-military-says-it-conducted-armed-patrols-joint-police-patrols-near-china-2024-08-26/</link><description>中国军方周一表示，随着缅甸执政军政府和叛军之间的战斗升级，中国军方已在中缅边境附近组织军队和空地警察联合巡逻，以维护安全稳定。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 00:43:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-military-says-it-conducted-armed-patrols-joint-police-patrols-near-china-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>中东局势升级担忧导致股市波动、油价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-26/</link><description>周一，世界股市变得谨慎，因为对美国即将加息的乐观情绪因对中东紧张局势加剧的担忧而减弱，油价上涨超过 1.5%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 00:22:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>尽管努力重建信任，中国与菲律宾在南海仍发生冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-philippines-clash-south-china-sea-despite-efforts-rebuild-trust-2024-08-25/</link><description>周日，菲律宾和中国在南中国海有争议的海域发生冲突，马尼拉称这是一次为渔民执行补给任务，这是该战略航道上一系列海空对抗中的最新一起。</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 10:33:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-philippines-clash-south-china-sea-despite-efforts-rebuild-trust-2024-08-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国银行行长刘金辞职</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/bank-china-president-liu-resigns-chairman-be-acting-president-2024-08-25/</link><description>中国银行表示，副董事长兼行长刘进因个人原因辞职，自周日起生效。</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 09:52:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/bank-china-president-liu-resigns-chairman-be-acting-president-2024-08-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国称对南海菲律宾船只采取“管控措施”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-it-took-control-measures-against-philippine-vessel-south-china-sea-2024-08-25/</link><description>中国周日表示，已对南海的一艘菲律宾船只采取“控制措施”，两国在南海争议海域的对抗不断升级。</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 07:51:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-it-took-control-measures-against-philippine-vessel-south-china-sea-2024-08-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>